<p>This is also a great feature. If Iâ€™m writing about something, Iâ€™ll appreciate a simple like or if you really liked the content a quick share with your pears. That would actually make my day. Now seriously, this is a precious feature. Everything a blogger wants is to get a little appreciation for the hard work. This is a great way for the reader to say â€¦thank youâ€œ.</p>

<p><strong>Moderation tools</strong></p>

<p>Iâ€™m not using this one, since I have my comments with some kind of login I think thatâ€™s enough, I choose to trust the community to be polite. Although if you need to moderate your comments you can do it, and the best thing is if you have 5 or even 10 blogs you do all the moderation in one place.</p>

<p><strong>Import and Export comments</strong></p>

<p>You are using other comment system and you are worried with what is going to happen to your comments already on that system like wordpress native comments system? Not to worry, you can do that just with a few clicks, is actually pretty easy.</p>

